    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行看到削减率在政策上降低了特朗普的异想天开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/ecb-seen-cutting-rate-twice-in-policy-beholden-to-trump-s-whims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博对经济学家的一项调查，欧洲中央银行官员可能最终从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）获得提示，但欧洲中央银行官员可能会再降低两次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/ecb-seen-cutting-rate-twice-in-policy-beholden-to-trump-s-whims</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库突然在警告特朗普的警告时突然交易像风险的资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的岩石固定安全性，美国国债债券在恐慌时期一直是投资者的首个征集港口。他们在9/11的全球金融危机期间集会，即使在美国自己的信用等级也被削减时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
