      <title>Monash IVF分享胚胎混合后的暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/monash-ivf-shares-plunge-after-embryo-mix-up-leads-to-birth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Monash IVF Group Ltd.周五下跌了多达30％，这是记录下最陡峭的日期下降，此前这家生殖医疗保健公司表示，属于一名患者的胚胎被错误地植入了另一名患者，导致儿童出生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/monash-ivf-shares-plunge-after-embryo-mix-up-leads-to-birth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 01:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
