      <title>尽管动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/philippines-says-to-keep-us-treasury-holdings-despite-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统不断发展的关税行动引发了全球金融市场的动荡，但菲律宾不会削减其对美国国债的持股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/philippines-says-to-keep-us-treasury-holdings-despite-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 01:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
